query:
INSERT INTO gtfs.feeds_updated (
                                                        onestop_feed_id, created_trips, updated_trips_time_ms
                                                    )
                                                    VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
                                                    ON CONFLICT (onestop_feed_id)
                                                    DO UPDATE SET created_trips = $2, updated_trips_time_ms = $3
